  "intent_precise": "0479ad-part-4.ot2.apiv2: Using input_plate (labware, slot cDNA at 4 Degrees C), reagent_plate (labware, slot Reagent Plate at 4 Degrees C). With Temperature Module module, Temperature Module module, magnetic module. (1) Wait 10 seconds. (2) Set temperature to 4\u00b0C. (3) Set temperature to 4\u00b0C. (4) Disengage magnets to release beads. (5) Pause: format (6) Transfer 10\u00b5L from source to destination. (7) Transfer 20\u00b5L from source to destination. (8) Pause: \nRemove cDNA plate for off-deck incubation\n    (lid 75, 20 degrees 30 min, 65 degrees 30 min, cool to 4 degrees).\n    Return plate and resume\n (9) Transfer 2\u00b5L from adapter 0 to destination A1. (10) Wait 1 seconds. (11) Wait 1 seconds. (12) Transfer 80\u00b5L from source to destination. (13) Pause: \nRemove cDNA plate for off-deck incubation\n    (20 degrees 15 min). Return plate and resume\n (14) Transfer 3\u00b5L from source to destination. (15) Transfer 20\u00b5L from source to destination.",
